if {getRake} == true:
	jump rake?
label rake?
[background arg="res://Assets/Backgrounds/Starlight_Forest.JPG" fade="0.0"]
join starlight center
starlight: Oh. Welcome back my friend. I did not think I would see you again so soon....
starlight: ....or ever really.
starlight: What can I help you with?
if {RAKE} == true:
	- So I found this rake...
		starlight: Oh?
		starlight: OH! That's Red's rake! I swore I gave that back to her.
		- It was in a field.
			starlight: In a field? Oh I must have left it there when I was doing my monthly raking!
			starlight: Oh that is absolutly horrible of me.
			starlight: That rake is a family heirloom of Red's you know?
			starlight: passed down through the family for 30 years
			starlight: It quite a nice rake. Red lends it to me for my monthly raking
			starlight: Oh she must have gotten herself all thrown into a knot cause of this...
			if {getRake} == true:
				- Yeah she is really mad.
					starlight: Oh I feel terrible. TERRIBLE I say.
					starlight: My friend you have to return it for me! I am affraid she will be quite upset with me. It might be best if she does not see me for a day or two.
					starlight: I'll apolagize in person than.
					- I can do that.
						starlight: You can? Excelant! Thank you so much my friend!
						starlight: I will not keep you. Many thanks go to you friend.
						set {StarlightRake} = true
						set {Starlight_Outcome} = "You checked in with Starlight. That meant more to her than you can realize."
						[end_timeline]
else:
	- Thought I would say hi
		starlight: Oh? Well Hi!
		starlight: It was nice to see you again my Friend.
		set {Starlight_Outcome} = "You checked in with Starlight. That meant more to her than you can realize."
		[end_timeline]